'''Bergen''' ([[Limburgtongo|Limburgt.]]: ''Baerge'') ben wan minti ini [[Limburgkondre]], taki ofisali wan provinsi fu [[Bakratongo]] ben leki a nen [[Limburg (Bakratongo)|Limburg]].

A [[presiplusplus]] ben [[Bergen (presi)|Bergen]]. Trawan funen presi ben [[Afferden]], [[Aijen]], [[Nieuw-Bergen]], [[Siebengewald]], [[Well]], [[Wellerlooi]], [[Heukelom]] nanga [[Knikkerdorp]].

A minti abi 110,20 [[km²]], pefu 4,17 km² watra, leki flaku nanga 13.652 man ini sin taki wan spredi gi fu 132 man ies km².

A net-teki ben 0485 nanga 0478 nanga a postukode ben {{stow enki}}. Funen autorustaru ben a N270 nanga N271.

A presi e abi wan stopulakidenki fu a delibaka ini a 19-100-yari.

